message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with sound and audio processing. cs.LG is also likely as it deals with machine learning and classification. cs.CV is less likely as the paper mentions that recent computer vision approaches against label noise are relatively complex, requiring complex networks or extra data resources, which is not the case in this paper. cs.CL and cs.AI are even less likely as they deal with natural language processing and general artificial intelligence, respectively, which are not directly related to the topic of this paper.
